profile:
Have you recently moved and would like your home locks rekeyed? Do you need a replacement keys for your vehicle? Does your business need service for the surveillance or access control system? Local Hamilton Locksmith is the locksmith company that can expertly handle that problems mentioned above along with any other locksmith or security issues.
Safe at Home
Keep your home and family safe and secure with Local Hamilton Locksmith. We can install or repair garage door and door locks, rekey locks. Do you have a lock in your home that has no key? Our expert Hamilton locksmiths can produce a replacement key. They can duplicate as many keys as you may need. Just give us a call to discuss your unique situation and one of our trained locksmiths will be glad to help you.
Business to Business
As business owners, we at Local Hamilton Locksmith understand how important it is to protect the assets of your company. That is why we have offer a comprehensive list of services for commercial customers. Local Locksmith in Hamilton can repair and service access control systems, surveillance systems and can design and install master key systems. Buzzer entry systems are another one of our areas of expertise along with the installation and repair of push-bar, door openers and closers.
Keep it Moving
Local Locksmith in Hamilton specializes in automotive locksmith needs. We can cut and program keys for any make and model of motorized vehicle. We can even cut and program high security keys and proximity keys. If you need extra key for you vehicle, we are the company to call. We can change or repair your ignition key and remove broken keys from the ignition. Our mobile Hamilton  locksmith units are fully equipped to provide any sort of automotive locksmith service, including motorcycles.
We Can Be There
You are locked out of your house with your young child inside. You are not home and your key breaks in your vehicle’s ignition. A lock is broken and your business is unsecured. These and many other emergencies can occur any hour of the day or night. Local Hamilton Locksmith  can handle any of these emergencies as we offer 24/7 emergency locksmith services.
